title: Hands Never Sleep - Stage Fractals EP MP3
description:
"The Illusionary Glance: Part I - Stage Fractals" EP is the first release by Hands Never Sleep since the release of several acoustic demos in 2009. These progressive-electronic compositions are four episodes pertaining to the "Illusionary" concept, which will be coupled with a full length by 2015. Thanks for downloading!
